{"id":4447,"date":"2018-04-30T17:57:00","date_gmt":"2018-04-30T21:57:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/staging.cegepsl.qc.ca\/nouvelle\/cegeps-en-spectacle-emile-tremblay-remporte-le-prix-studio-jupiter\/"},"modified":"2023-06-14T13:18:56","modified_gmt":"2023-06-14T17:18:56","slug":"cegeps-en-spectacle-emile-tremblay-remporte-le-prix-studio-jupiter","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/nouvelle\/cegeps-en-spectacle-emile-tremblay-remporte-le-prix-studio-jupiter\/","title":{"rendered":"C\u00e9geps en spectacle : \u00c9mile Tremblay remporte le prix Studio Jupiter"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>\u00c9mile Tremblay, \u00e9tudiant du programme Techniques de musique et chanson, a m\u00e9rit\u00e9 le prix Studio Jupiter lors de la finale nationale de la 39e \u00e9dition du concours C\u00e9geps en spectacle.\u00a0Le prix Studio Jupiter consiste en deux enregistrements sonores pour deux artistes ou groupes, ainsi que 25 heures chacun d\u2019acc\u00e8s \u00e0 un studio.<\/p>\n<p>Le Coll\u00e8ge tient \u00e0 f\u00e9liciter <strong>\u00c9mile Tremblay<\/strong> pour sa performance dans le cadre du concours artistique annuel qu&rsquo;est C\u00e9geps en spectacle. Vous pouvez d&rsquo;ailleurs la voir sur <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=vXitlRvaPdA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">YouTube<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"39e \u00e9dition de C\u00e9geps en spectacle - \u00c9mile - C\u00e9gep de Saint-Laurent\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/vXitlRvaPdA?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe><\/p>\n<p>\u00a0<\/p>\n<p>Cette ann\u00e9e, les grands gagnants du concours sont :<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Premier prix : Alexandra Catus alias <a href=\"https:\/\/riasq.us7.list-manage.com\/track\/click?u=0c51e6ae7f084f4462d34deb1&#038;id=2930a87170&#038;e=f7b6518d75\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>Marino<\/strong><\/a> du <strong>Coll\u00e8ge de Rosemont<\/strong><\/li>\n<li>Deuxi\u00e8me prix :\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/riasq.us7.list-manage.com\/track\/click?u=0c51e6ae7f084f4462d34deb1&#038;id=9d7a7c5acd&#038;e=f7b6518d75\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>M\u00e9gan Brouillard<\/strong><\/a> du <strong>C\u00e9gep de Saint-Hyacinthe<\/strong><\/li>\n<li>Prix Cr\u00e9ation :\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/riasq.us7.list-manage.com\/track\/click?u=0c51e6ae7f084f4462d34deb1&#038;id=42c5e7de67&#038;e=f7b6518d75\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>Sophia Chan Kong R. et Alexandra Negru<\/strong><\/a> de l\u2019<strong>\u00c9cole de musique Vincent-d\u2019Indy<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>\u00a0<\/p>\n<p>La Direction des communications<\/p>\n<p>\u00a0<\/p>\n<p>\u00a0<\/p>\n<p>\u00a0<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u00c9mile Tremblay, \u00e9tudiant du programme Techniques de musique et chanson, a m\u00e9rit\u00e9 le prix Studio Jupiter lors de la finale nationale de la 39e \u00e9dition du concours C\u00e9geps en spectacle.\u00a0<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":4449,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[15],"sujet-actualite":[196],"etiquette-interne":[2301,2303],"class_list":["post-4447","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-nouvelle","sujet-actualite-honneurs","etiquette-interne-honneurs","etiquette-interne-musique"],"acf":[],"publishpress_future_action":{"enabled":false,"date":"2026-05-05 21:16:34","action":"change-status","newStatus":"draft","terms":[],"taxonomy":"category"},"publishpress_future_workflow_manual_trigger":{"enabledWorkflows":[]},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4447","targetHints":{"al